@blurHY: Mostly, Xiaoping's market socialism.
Some people just call it state capitalism, though, because it's based on Lenin's NEP. The Idea that, in order to have socialism, a country MUST go through capitalism in order to develop the working forces and industries.
Lenin did it because Russia was agrarian feudalism (not capitalism), so did Xiaoping. There were no means of production to seize
